title: Hawley and Gillibrand team up to ban lawmakers and officials from owning stock
description: Sens. Kirsten Gillibrand (D-NY) and Josh Hawley (R-MO) unveiled legislation on Wednesday to bar lawmakers and members of the executive branch from owning stock in individual companies.

title: Bills propose audit of Cannabis Control Commission
description: (The Center Square) – Legislators sitting on the Joint Committee on Cannabis Policy on Tuesday heard testimony supporting bills proposing audits of the Cannabis Control Commission.
